snippet.title: Let’s Sing 2022 | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Let’s Sing is back and this time on the new generation! Grab a microphone, some friends and join the hottest karaoke game of the year!

We will have more information coming soon like track list, release date and MORE!
